                            <comment id="14127117" author="clebertsuconic" created="Tue, 9 Sep 2014 15:36:45 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;do you still set maxFrameSize on the transport?&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;p&gt;I found out that not setting it at all will make performance to be 10X better due to some issues on Proton. It&apos;s a bug on Proton probably and still not fixed.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
